{"blogid": "124450611", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "5", "writerCollect": "9", "writerComment": "1", "writerFan": "0", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "67", "writerName": "不太正经的人想正经", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_124450611.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "135268", "writerRankWeekly": "56997", "writerThumb": "6", "writerVisitNum": "3312", "blog_read_count": "1516", "blog_time": "已于 2022-04-27 14:59:33 修改", "blog_title": "关于MySQL报sql_mode=only_full_group_by的解决方法", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-dark\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h1><a id=\"_0\"></a>报错页面信息</h1>\n<p>大概意思是说：语法错误或访问冲突，表达式不在GROUP BY的条件中，并且这与<mark>sql_mode=only_full_group_by</mark>不兼容</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\e2a973601a4b405499924ce7e8fa5857.png\"/><br/> 这个错误发生在mysql 5.7.5 版本及以上版本会出现的问题：<br/> mysql 5.7.5版本以上默认的sql配置是:sql_mode=“ONLY_FULL_GROUP_BY”，这个配置严格执行了\"SQL92标准\"。<br/> 很多从5.6升级到5.7时，为了语法兼容，大部分都会选择调整sql_mode，使其保持跟5.6一致，为了尽量兼容程序。</p>\n<h2><a id=\"Windows_8\"></a>Windows下的解决办法</h2>\n<p>修改mysql的配置文件 my.ini</p>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ab546ba2dea24ca0873f5d541be8eeff.png\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这里要注意一下：把这句话要放在 【mysqld】这个分类下，否则不会生效。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">#解决GROUP BY</span>\nsql_mode<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token constant\">STRICT_TRANS_TABLES</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token constant\">NO_ZERO_IN_DATE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token constant\">NO_ZERO_DATE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token constant\">ERROR_FOR_DIVISION_BY_ZERO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token constant\">NO_ENGINE_SUBSTITUTION</span>\n\n</code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>保存编辑后重启mysql即可；<br/> 如果重启失败的话把 <mark>NO_AUTO_CREATE_USER</mark> 这个属性去掉即可</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>我这里只记录了Windows下的解决方法 ， 如果有起其他问题可以参考原创大佬</strong></p>\n<h3><a id=\"___httpsblogcsdnnetu012660464articledetails113977173_25\"></a>尊重原创!!! https://blog.csdn.net/u012660464/article/details/113977173</h3>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>", "first_tag": "PHP", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 1, "php": 1, "time": "2022-04-27 14:59:33", "summary": "报错页面信息大概意思是说：语法错误或访问冲突，表达式不在的条件中，并且这与不兼容在这里插入图片描述这个错误发生在版本及以上版本会出现的问题：版本以上默认的配置是，这个配置严格执行了标准。很多从升级到时"}